CatDescriptText: Cutline of image published in Pittsburgh Courier newspaper, April 25, 1959, pg 14 reads: "Paper Counter - Edward J. Meade, floor clerk (left), and Richard D. Kennedy, special clerk, waiting on record searchers."
TitMainTitle: Edward J. Meade and Richard D. Kennedy wearing patterned necktie, filling out cards for men and women standing at counter, in Allegheny County Prothonotary Office
